column5: Ashley Rae was out with us for a day of hardwater walleye fishing on the Bay of Quinte.  She caught her first walleye through the ice that day.  Correction, she caught her first 5 walleyes through the ice that day!  One of which broke the 10lb mark.  Here is a video of her day.  http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1ttW4QDmxNY  Jeff
You got to love catching them big eyes from the BOQ Awesome video Jeff and thanks for sharing Leechman
